Did I cause you any trouble?

525
00:34:28,200 --> 00:34:30,200
No trouble.

526
00:34:30,200 --> 00:34:31,200
But just now..

527
00:34:31,200 --> 00:34:32,800
Well,

528
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:37,400
you just came back, you should go back and unpack. I'll meet you tonight.

529
00:34:40,100 --> 00:34:41,600
- Then I'll be going.
- Okay.

530
00:34:41,600 --> 00:34:43,900
Don't miss me too much.

531
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:47,000
Be careful on your way back.

532
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:54,400
Try this, too.

533
00:34:55,100 --> 00:34:56,800
Hello, everyone. May I have your attention, please?

534
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:59,500
Let me introduce a new colleague.

535
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:02,200
Hi, everyone. My name is Mo Fei.

536
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:06,200
I'm the assistant for Teacher Cheng. Please look after me.

537
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:11,000
That's it?

538
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:14,600
Mo Fei, you're too modest. Say some more.

539
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:16,000
I don't have much to say.

540
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:19,200
Okay, I'll speak for Mo Fei. She's my junior.

541
00:35:19,200 --> 00:35:22,000
She's very devoted to Chinese Fashion.

542
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:26,000
