543
00:35:26,700 --> 00:35:28,800
That's too exaggerating.

544
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:30,600
I'm excited.

545
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:34,400
Mo Fei, I recognize you. You participated in Mingyuan's competition.

546
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:37,600
You're the designer of the "Old tea-horse road."

547
00:35:37,600 --> 00:35:39,400
It was well liked.

548
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:41,600
It's even better than award-winning works.

549
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:43,200
Thanks for everyone's praise.

550
00:35:43,200 --> 00:35:45,400
I am still in the learning stage.

551
00:35:45,400 --> 00:35:48,100
I hope we can make progress together.

552
00:35:48,100 --> 00:35:50,800
You're too modest. With designs like yours,

553
00:35:50,800 --> 00:35:54,200
your works have won market recognition. Unlike some people,

554
00:35:54,200 --> 00:35:57,000
grades are average. Abilities are average, too.

555
00:35:57,000 --> 00:36:00,000
Besides flattering others, they're not good at anything.

556
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,200
Enough.

557
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:03,000
Come.

558
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:04,600
