559
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:08,100
Today, let's talk about the meeting's main topic.

560
00:36:08,100 --> 00:36:09,800
When do we need it finalized?

561
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:12,400
The faster the better.

562
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:15,000
But there're some details we need to focus on.

563
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,200
What details?

564
00:36:16,200 --> 00:36:18,400
To reveal the splash-ink method.

565
00:36:22,600 --> 00:36:24,600
Look at this.

566
00:36:43,200 --> 00:36:45,200
Director Xia! Director Xia!

567
00:36:45,200 --> 00:36:46,300
Why are you so flustered?

568
00:36:46,300 --> 00:36:49,800
Cheng Yang got a new assistant.

569
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:53,000
She's my college schoolmate, Mo Fei.

570
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:56,000
