571
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:59,200
They are in love and want to see each other all the time.

572
00:36:59,200 --> 00:37:02,000
These thoughts are nor—

573
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:04,200
I-It's normal.

574
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:07,140
Scared me.

575
00:37:07,140 --> 00:37:09,400
My goodness. Girls are too scary.

576
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:13,600
Take these art books and seek some inspiration.

577
00:37:13,600 --> 00:37:16,600
You can come to me anytime when you have any.

578
00:37:16,600 --> 00:37:18,400
Okay?

579
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:23,600
What happened?

580
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,600
Nothing.

581
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:27,800
I just wanted to say...

582
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:32,000
does Director Xia know I'm here helping you?

583
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:36,800
She doesn't know. Why?

584
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:40,800
I'm scared that I will cause you trouble.

585
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:42,400
Cause what trouble?

586
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:44,400
I wrote it clearly in the contract.

587
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:47,200
I have the power to pick my own assistant.

588
00:37:48,400 --> 00:37:51,300
Then that's fine. I'll go over there.

589
00:37:51,300 --> 00:37:53,000
Wait.

590
00:37:54,200 --> 00:37:56,480
You're acting strange today.

591
00:37:56,480 --> 00:37:58,600
Do you have jet lag?

592
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:04,400
Are you trying to go meet President Tang as soon as possible?

593
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:08,200
Shouldn't you thank me for this opportunity?

594
00:38:08,200 --> 00:38:12,300
Since you already know, you still assign me so much work.

595
00:38:12,300 --> 00:38:15,000
I might see Duoduo and tell on you.

596
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,800
Don't.

597
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:20,200
Don't tell Duoduo. I'm just joking.

598
00:38:20,200 --> 00:38:22,100
I know.

599
00:38:34,800 --> 00:38:36,200
Mo Fei!

600
