- Jiaxi!
- I missed you.

601
00:38:38,600 --> 00:38:41,000
Long time no see. I miss you so much.

602
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:43,600
Freshly squeezed juice just for the amazing you.

603
00:38:43,600 --> 00:38:44,600
Thanks.

